summary: Relating to the Seattle Shoreline Master Program, Chapter 23.60 of the Seattle Municipal Code (SMC); amending Section 23.60.014 to add the Lake Union Construction Limit Line provisions from SMC Chapter 24.82; amending Sections 23.60.014 and 23.60.156 to delete the reference to Title 24; and amending Sections 23.60.368 and 23.60.633 to correct errors and omissions.
committee: Housing, Community Development and Urban Environment
